chandra''\n\n== See also ==\n\n* [[List of Indian television actors]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb name|4468244|Arun Govil}}\n*{{Twitter|Arungovil12}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Govil, Arun}}\n[[Category:Indian male film actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Bengali cinema]]\n[[Category:Indian male television actors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1948 births]]\n[[Category:People from Meerut]]\n[[Category:Chaudhary Charan Singh University alumni]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Indian actor}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Arun Govil\n| image = ArunGovil.jpg\n| caption =Govil in 2009\n| birth_name  = Arun Govil\n| birth_date = 30 October<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/birthday-wishes-amit-navina-yash-and-arun|title=Birthday wishes for Amit, Navina, Yash and Arun|date=2012-10-30|website= Tellychakkar Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-18}}</ref>\n| birth_place = [[Meerut]], [[Uttar Pradesh]], [[India]]\n| nationality =  Indian\n| alma_mater   = [[Chaudhary Charan Singh University]]\n| occupation = {{hlist|Actor|producer}}\n| years_active       = 1977- Present\n| known_for          = [[Rama]] in<br>[[Ramayan (1987 TV series)|Ramayan (1987)]]\n| spouse = Shrilekha Govil\n| children = 2\n| relatives =[[Tabassum (actress)|Tabassum]] (sister-in-law)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rediff.com/movies/report/i-never-became-a-big-heroine-tabassum/20141029.htm|title=Nargis, Meena Kumari, Madhubala, Suraiya... they all loved me|website=www.rediff.com|access-date=2018-11-11}}</ref>\n}}\n'''Arun Govil''' is an [[India]]n actor and producer.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/birthday-wishes-amit-navina-yash-and-arun|title=Birthday wishes for Amit, Navina, Yash and Arun|date=2012-10-30|website= Tellychakkar Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-18}}</ref><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=